 {"id":"frankenjax-e0a6","title":"Replace AD unsupported-primitive placeholder wording","description":"mock-code-finder audit found crates/fj-ad/src/lib.rs renders AdError::UnsupportedPrimitive as 'AD not implemented for primitive: <name>'. This unsupported derivative path is a real fail-closed contract, but the phrase 'not implemented' looks like placeholder/stub code and is not currently covered by the no-stub regression display guard. Replace the message with explicit unsupported-primitive wording and extend crates/fj-conformance/tests/no_stub_regression.rs to ban generic 'not implemented' and cover AdError::UnsupportedPrimitive display so future placeholder wording cannot silently re-enter.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2026-04-28T19:41:26.436810893Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-28T19:45:53.868411774Z","closed_at":"2026-04-28T19:45:53.866599381Z","close_reason":"Replaced AD unsupported primitive placeholder wording and extended no_stub_regression to ban generic not-implemented wording.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
